OL,3,CJohn Swinney leads tributes after SNP
OL,4,Cminister Christina McKelvie dies aged
OL,5,C57
OL,7,FFirst Minister John Swinney has led
OL,8,Fheartfelt tributes to Scottish
OL,9,Fgovernment minister Christina McKelvie
OL,10,Ffollowing her death at the age of 57,
OL,11,Fremembering her as a "kind, loyal, and
OL,12,Ffun-loving colleague".
OL,14,FThe drugs and alcohol minister took
OL,15,Fmedical leave last summer after
OL,16,Fannouncing she had secondary breast
OL,17,Fcancer.
