OL,7,FMcKelvie's partner and SNP deputy
OL,8,Fleader Keith Brown, announced her
OL,9,Fdeath in a statement on Thursday
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,12,F"To us, she was our beloved mum,
OL,13,Fpartner and gran to Maeve and Leo," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"She was always hard working and
OL,17,Fenthusiastic and lit up every room she
OL,18,Fwas in with her positivity and bright
OL,19,Fsmile."
