OL,7,FPresiding Officer Alison Johnstone
OL,8,Fordered the flags outside the Scottish
OL,9,FParliament to fly at half-mast and
OL,10,Fannounced plans for a book of
OL,11,Fcondolences to be opened on Thursday
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,14,FA tearful Ms Johnstone led the
OL,15,Ftributes in the chamber, speaking of
OL,16,Fthe "warm welcome" she received from
OL,17,FMs McKelvie when she first became an
OL,18,FMSP in 2011.
