OL,7,FAn emotional First Minister John
OL,8,FSwinney then told MSPs: "Today is an
OL,9,Funbearably sad day as we come to terms
OL,10,Fwith the loss of our generous, kind,
OL,11,Floyal and fun-loving colleague
OL,12,FChristina McKelvie.
OL,14,F"Members across this Parliament will
OL,15,Ffeel that loss, but my party is aching
OL,16,Fat the news today," The SNP leader
OL,17,Fadded, calling McKelvie a "magnificent
OL,18,Fwoman".
