OL,4,Cminister Christina McKelvie dies aged
OL,5,C57
OL,7,FOriginally from the Easterhouse area
OL,8,Fof Glasgow, Ms McKelvie was elected as
OL,9,Fan MSP in 2007 before winning the
OL,10,Fconstituency in 2011.
OL,12,FShe was a minister in the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment for seven years, serving as
OL,14,Fequalities minister between 2018 and
OL,15,F2023, and then culture minister before
OL,16,Fmoving into her most recent role.
OL,18,FShe recovered from breast cancer in
OL,19,F2021, but announced last June that she
OL,20,Fhad been diagnosed with secondary
OL,21,Fbreast cancer.
