OL,7,FEarlier this year, she announced her
OL,8,Fintention to stand down as an MSP.
OL,10,FFormer first minister Nicola Sturgeon
OL,11,F- who first appointed Ms McKelvie as a
OL,12,Fminister ` paid tribute to her
OL,13,F"beautiful friend" in a post on
OL,14,FInstagram.
OL,16,F"It is going to take a very long time
OL,17,Ffor those of us who love her to come
OL,18,Fto terms with the passing this morning
OL,19,Fof our friend and colleague Christina
OL,20,FMcKelvie MSP.
