OL,7,F"As a politician, her ability to
OL,8,Fconnect with people on a very human
OL,9,Flevel and understand instinctively the
OL,10,Fchallenges they were facing was her
OL,11,Fsuperpower.
OL,13,F"She had the biggest heart of anyone I
OL,14,Fhave ever known. I will never forget
OL,15,Fthe friendship and kindness she showed
OL,16,Fme over many years."
OL,18,FTributes were also paid by Holyrood
OL,19,Fleaders during a muted session of
OL,20,FFirst Minister's Questions on Thursday.
