OL,7,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,8,FFindlay described Ms McKelvie as a
OL,9,F"respected colleague and a dedicated
OL,10,Fpublic servant".
OL,12,FMeanwhile Scottish Labour leader Anas
OL,13,FSarwar said the pain of her death will
OL,14,Fbe felt "across the Parliament", and
OL,15,Fthat: "Across all parties, many have
OL,16,Flost a friend."
