OL,7,FScottish Green co-leader Patrick
OL,8,FHarvie ` who previously served in
OL,9,Fgovernment alongside Ms McKelvie `
OL,10,Fdescribed her as "the best of us".
OL,12,FStifling tears, Mr Harvie added:
OL,13,F"Today is a moment of pain and
OL,14,Fsadness. But Christina's life and her
OL,15,Fextraordinary spirit deserve to be
OL,16,Fcelebrated."
OL,18,FHe went on to ask the First Minister
OL,19,Fhow MSPs "can all bring that
OL,20,Fcompassion and kindness into our work,
OL,21,Fas Christina did?"
